    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#bin_to_list/1" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">bin_to_list(Subject)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Converts <code class="inline">Subject</code> to a list of <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:byte/0"><code class="inline">byte()</code></a>s, each
representing the value of one byte.</p></div>

