<code class="inline">Pattern</code> with <code class="inline">Replacement</code> if given as a literal
<a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:binary/0"><code class="inline">binary/0</code></a> or with the result of applying
<code class="inline">Replacement</code> to a matching subpart if given as a <code class="inline">fun</code>.</p></div>

    </div>


      <div class="summary-row">
