        <a href="#split/3" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">split(Subject, Pattern, Options)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Splits <code class="inline">Subject</code> into a list of binaries based on <code class="inline">Pattern</code>.</p></div>

