  <section class="docstring">



        <div class="specs">

            <pre translate="no"><span class="attribute">-spec</span> join([<a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:binary/0">binary</a>()], <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:binary/0">binary</a>()) -> <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:binary/0">binary</a>().</pre>

        </div>


<p>Joins a list of binaries together by a specified <code class="inline">Separator</code>.</p><p>Equivalent to <code class="inline">iolist_to_binary(lists:join(Separator, Binaries))</code>, but faster.</p><h2 id="join/2-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#join/2-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">binary</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">join</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-2">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-3">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;a&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-3">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-4">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;b&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-4">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-5">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;c&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-5">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-2">]</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-6">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;, &quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-6">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-7">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">&quot;a, b, c&quot;</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2831170554-7">&gt;&gt;</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
